{"tid":792911,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"中意養蟹同螺既巴絲入一入黎","createTime":"2018-08-25T02:46:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T11:04:18.000Z","uid":161343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"62abd4ae2779175ce6aff5f49aa830d218569fa7","tid":792911,"uid":161343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T02:46:18.000Z","msg":"小弟有養開蟹 係金魚街買 <br />\n覺得係金魚街賣既蟹都係垃圾！<br />\n最近又對螺有興趣 又係好少地方有得賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲知唔知香港邊度有多d或者特別d既蟹同螺賣<br />\n小弟同蝦無乜興趣 <br />\n暫時只知元朗有間(一水族)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"368cc7c11c502c2ca172c0d586a75f6de309604b","tid":792911,"uid":161343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T03:02:27.000Z","msg":"暫時見過既蟹有惡魔蟹 辣椒蟹 紅豆蟹 斑點蟹 <br />\n螺就有黑金剛螺 殺手螺 利申新手唔係識好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d1cf3490205097512cb0c853a77439fb7ca797a","tid":792911,"uid":161343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T03:03:13.000Z","msg":"有冇人有養開 一齊交流下 唔好淨係養魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a584a971f5622b970949076fab046f8c4737c23","tid":792911,"uid":759,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"368cc7c11c502c2ca172c0d586a75f6de309604b","tid":792911,"uid":161343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T03:02:27.000Z","msg":"暫時見過既蟹有惡魔蟹 辣椒蟹 紅豆蟹 斑點蟹 <br />\n螺就有黑金剛螺 殺手螺 利申新手唔係識好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T03:06:56.000Z","msg":"我見過薑蔥炒蟹,豉椒炒蟹,刺身蟹,凍蟹<br />\n螺就白烚螺,辣酒煮花螺"},{"pid":"2b379afc29b732343f8c9dcd4d22873a7bc9006d","tid":792911,"uid":161343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T03:07:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/110639_123c3f9f54183705c978efc92603dd95.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ese